Still, you're most likely looking at at least 6k dead.

snippet.textDisplay: Exactly what happened.   In the year 2020, it came back with a vengeance in the form of coronavirus, which  is infecting thousands of people and hundreds die in just a short time.  Right now they are trying to find a cure and to contain this virus.   I thought after SARS, they would think twice about letting wildlife market come back, but apparently no one was monitoring it.   The wildlife market survived, bringing in another form of virus which is just as deadly as the SARS virus.  I wish them luck.   My question is why do they have to eat those wildlife animals, don't they have enough domesticated animal meat to eat???
